Deriving Energy from Gravity is a Weakest Foundational Force Solution.

Graviton Dams at Graviton Rivers:
waterfalls, grain dispensers, conveyor belt termini.
Gravoelectric possibilities pale before the vision of fusion.
Yet, obtainable. Conceivable. Sustainable?
Base-camp of humanity need not permanent, though our lasting future starts here.

